    {
        "SurahNumber": 46,
        "AyahNumber": 27,
        "Tafseer": "\"And We have already destroyed what surrounds you of [other] cities, and We have diversified the signs that perhaps they would return.\" (27)\n\nAnother Warning to the Quraysh\n\nThis addresses the Quraysh. It states: if you consider the story of 'Aad far-off, look at the settlements in your surroundings. To remove the veils from their eyes and hearts, We presented Our signs in various forms so that they returned to their Creator, but they also refused to accept Our signs, which resulted in Our destroying them. This points to those destroyed settlements by which the Quraysh passed in their commercial journeys."
